---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Walk in the Spirit">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-16">
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-8">Walk in the Spirit</h1>
    <div class="prose prose-lg dark:prose-invert max-w-4xl">
      <p class="lead text-xl text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-300">
        To walk in the Spirit means to surrender daily to the RUACH HAQODESH, allowing Him to lead, guide, and empower you in all things.
      </p>
      
      <h2>What Does It Mean?</h2>
      <p>
        Galatians 5:16 says, "Walk in the Spirit, and you shall not fulfill the lust of the flesh." This is not a suggestionâ€”it's a command. The Spirit-filled life is the only way to overcome the flesh and live in victory.
      </p>
      
      <h2>Daily Consecration</h2>
      <p>
        Walking in the Spirit requires daily consecration. Each morning, you must:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Surrender your will to YAHUAH</li>
        <li>Seek His face in prayer</li>
        <li>Read and meditate on His Word</li>
        <li>Listen for His voice throughout the day</li>
        <li>Obey promptly when He speaks</li>
      </ul>
      
      <h2>The Fruit of the Spirit</h2>
      <p>
        When you walk in the Spirit, His fruit will manifest in your life: love, joy, peace, patience, kindness, goodness, faithfulness, gentleness, and self-control (Galatians 5:22-23).
      </p>
      
      <h2>Recommended Resources</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 not-prose mt-6">
        <a href="/prayer-and-fasting" class="block p-4 bg-white dark:bg-neutral-800 rounded-lg border border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-700 hover:border-blue-600 dark:hover:border-blue-400 transition-colors">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Prayer & Fasting</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-300">Sharpen your spiritual senses</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/spiritual-warfare" class="block p-4 bg-white dark:bg-neutral-800 rounded-lg border border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-700 hover:border-blue-600 dark:hover:border-blue-400 transition-colors">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Spiritual Warfare</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-300">Fight in the Spirit's power</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Base>

